name: CELLY
description:
32 Bit Jam 2022 Entry (v1)
[A] - Left. [D] - Right. [Space] - Jump. [Shift] - Run

Celly is a tiny creature who lives under the ice on Saturn's 6th moon, Enceladus.

Not shown in the game: Celly is blasted from the moon in a giant ice geyser, and makes his way to Earth, where he inspires a young H.P. Lovecraft to write about Cthulhu!

A little buggy, but still kind of fun. :)
